data.enText: no longer useful because of being old-fashioned

data.chText: 这些数字现在已经过时。

value.def: If you describe something as outdated, you mean that you think it is old-fashioned and no longer useful or relevant to modern life.

example.ex: Caryl Churchill's play about Romania is already outdated.
example.tran: 卡里尔·丘吉尔关于罗马尼亚的戏剧已经过时了。

value.tran: 过时的；陈旧的；老式的；废弃的
